  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the oats and soak them in water for 30 minutes.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a medium saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the soaked oats and 1 cup of water to the saucepan.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped mint leaves, salt, and lemon juice.",
    "Garnish with chopped green onion and serve warm."
